Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.46,0:00:06.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Here you go... your Manhattan.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.49,0:00:08.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what about my red cherry?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.96,0:00:09.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.13,0:00:13.39,Default,,0,0,0,,There should be a red cherry in it,\Nor it isn't a Manhattan!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.20,0:00:15.67,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Sorry about that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.33,0:00:17.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Humph! You'd better watch it.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.61,0:00:28.87,Default,,0,0,0,,My business goes well\Nwhen I have this in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.25,0:00:30.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.15,0:00:32.91,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a jinx, a jinx!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:05.60,Monster - Time and Place,,0,0,0,,{\pos(365,270)\fad(712,635)}Verden, (Germany)
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.06,0:02:05.60,Monster - Time and Place,,0,0,0,,{\pos(365,325)\fad(900,671)\fs37}Springer Estate
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.64,0:02:10.56,Title,,0,0,0,,{\pos(362,350)\fad(1021,918)}A Past Erased
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.69,0:02:11.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.42,0:02:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Let there still be something\Nof value left!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.97,0:02:27.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, okay... It's just as I thought...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:27.90,0:02:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Everything's right here;\Nlike a candy store.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.04,0:02:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Is there anything\Nvaluable enough for me?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.91,0:02:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Life is fleeting. He may have been\Ntouted as a candidate for governor,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.62,0:02:44.74,Default,,0,0,0,,but when he and his wife\Nwere gunned down together like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.42,0:02:47.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Oops, I'd better get down\Nto business...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.99,0:02:52.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I figure the safe must be\Nin this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.10,0:03:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-Wh-Wh-What's with this chill?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.27,0:03:04.33,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the first time\NI've felt anything so repulsive...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.77,0:03:08.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Someone's in this room...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.58,0:03:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No way! What am I so scared about?\NIt's not like me...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.22,0:03:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.15,0:03:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Raise your hands over your head!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.49,0:03:24.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, no... He was behind me. Crap...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.56,0:03:27.72,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all because that bartender\Nforgot the cherry...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.23,0:03:29.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and raise your hands!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.43,0:03:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,All right, all right...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.07,0:03:36.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break, officer.\NI haven't taken anything yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.60,0:03:38.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.14,0:03:40.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh? What the...? You're one of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.84,0:03:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,In that case, why don't you\Nput that scary thing away and...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.31,0:03:45.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Put your hands on your head!!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:48.11,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with this guy?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.35,0:03:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,He seems harder to deal with\Nthan the police.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:55.25,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's the cops!\NYou fouled up, didn't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.36,0:03:56.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm getting outta here!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.06,0:03:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.63,0:04:01.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody like you\Nwill just slow me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.83,0:04:03.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn you!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.57,0:04:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't follow me, I said!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.33,0:04:08.83,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn! This is just not my day!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.14,0:04:15.23,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...\NI thought you looked familiar...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.44,0:04:16.57,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the guy in the newspaper...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.78,0:04:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the doctor who's\Nthe “person of interest”
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.41,0:04:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,in the Councilman Springer\Nmurder case.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.78,0:04:21.91,Default,,0,0,0,,And you're a thief?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.08,0:04:26.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Exactly! Unlike you, I wouldn't do\Nanything senseless like killing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.59,0:04:29.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know anything about the killing\Nthat took place in that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.76,0:04:33.16,Default,,0,0,0,,No idea. Hurry up and get out\Nof my face, will you? So long.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.27,0:04:39.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.37,0:04:43.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You're supposed to be\Na top-notch surgeon, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.64,0:04:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,My brilliant brain just came up\Nwith an idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.08,0:04:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you think that meetings\Nhappen by chance, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.85,0:04:52.11,Default,,0,0,0,,They don't, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.25,0:04:55.38,Default,,0,0,0,,All meetings between people\Nare determined beforehand...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.88,0:04:58.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You and I were destined\Nto become a team.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.09,0:05:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.15,0:05:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,The underworld is full of people\Nwho need someone like you;
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.23,0:05:06.52,Default,,0,0,0,,people who want to call a doctor,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.59,0:05:09.19,Default,,0,0,0,,but die because\Nthe danger is too great.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.10,0:05:12.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave the management\Nto me... Heckel!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.73,0:05:15.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll make you into the best doctor\Nof the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.14,0:05:18.30,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd make a whole lot more\Nin the underworld.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.47,0:05:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll be a billionaire\Nbefore you know it...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.28,0:05:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Doctor! Where are you going?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:26.97,Default,,0,0,0,,There's something I have to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.72,0:05:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.52,0:05:32.35,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know about the murders\Nin that house, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.59,0:05:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.32,0:05:37.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, I saw the Killer, you see...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.63,0:05:38.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What's that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.63,0:05:41.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you talking about?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.63,0:05:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,You want to know?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.00,0:05:46.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Wasn't he blond\Nand about 20 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.80,0:05:47.89,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.37,0:05:50.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, just tell me about that killer!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.21,0:05:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll tell you if you'll team up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.34,0:05:58.07,Default,,0,0,0,,He's on the third floor\Nof this cheap apartment house.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.15,0:06:00.61,Default,,0,0,0,,How do you know this?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.18,0:06:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,After I set my sights\Non that councilman's house,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.38,0:06:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,I spent about a month researching it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.49,0:06:08.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Just when I was set to go,\Nthat guy showed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.82,0:06:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,When I looked in the window,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.16,0:06:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,the councilman\Nand his wife were dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.39,0:06:17.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I figured I could squeeze some money\Nout of the killer, so I followed him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.46,0:06:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, this proves that\Nyou're innocent in this case.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.14,0:06:23.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Go phone it in to the police\Nif that's what you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.17,0:06:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Then you and I can go somewhere
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.31,0:06:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,and sit and talk over a drink\Nabout our dream-like future...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.24,0:06:31.21,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.45,0:06:34.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you want to see him for?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.92,0:06:38.18,Default,,0,0,0,,He's a murderer, you know!\NYou'll get yourself killed!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.75,0:06:41.59,Default,,0,0,0,,What is he thinking?!\NI can't keep up with him!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.73,0:06:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,But it's not often I'll find\Na source of revenue like him.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.57,0:06:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I make it a rule not to\Nstick my neck out, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.63,0:07:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.16,0:07:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,It's another hot day, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.23,0:07:29.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually, I'm looking for\Na certain person...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.41,0:07:33.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor, are you alive?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.08,0:07:36.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.88,0:07:40.11,Default,,0,0,0,,You fool! He's got a gun!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.91,0:07:44.35,Default,,0,0,0,,I often used to go walking\Nwith my mother...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.15,0:07:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.89,0:07:50.85,Default,,0,0,0,,... along the sunflower field...\Non summer days like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.93,0:07:55.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, she died a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.83,0:08:01.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Didn't you use that gun\Nat someone's request? Some man...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.27,0:08:07.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Man...? Oh... One day,\Nhe approached in a bar.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.04,0:08:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,A blond man, about 20 years old?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.24,0:08:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.28,0:08:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. He had a beautiful smile,\Nthat Erich.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.85,0:08:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So he's Erich, now...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.85,0:08:22.48,Default,,0,0,0,,We met a few times\Nand became good friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.09,0:08:28.03,Default,,0,0,0,,He invited me to his home...\Nto Councilman Springer's home.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.56,0:08:30.69,Default,,0,0,0,,He lived in that mansion\Nuntil recently?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.27,0:08:36.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. He said they took good care of him,\Nlike a son, since about a year ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.24,0:08:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, I had my eye on that home\Nfor a month,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.21,0:08:41.47,Default,,0,0,0,,but I never saw anybody like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.28,0:08:45.61,Default,,0,0,0,,They were a wonderful family.\NHere's a picture...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.25,0:08:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,That's me and the Councilman\Nand his wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.38,0:08:52.68,Default,,0,0,0,,But there was something\NI just couldn't forgive them for.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.92,0:08:59.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There was a bed of sunflowers\Non their property,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.29,0:09:03.23,Default,,0,0,0,,but he tore it up in order to\Nbuild a parking area.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.47,0:09:09.10,Default,,0,0,0,,When I said that was\Nan awful thing to do, Erich agreed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.94,0:09:12.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-You don't mean\Nyou killed them over that!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.64,0:09:17.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides, Erich told me...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.54,0:09:20.10,Default,,0,0,0,,that Councilman Springer\Nhad a mistress.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.45,0:09:23.31,Default,,0,0,0,,He also said this.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.88,0:09:28.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I no longer want to be\Na member of the Springers' family.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.82,0:09:35.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not a member of that family.”\NThen he asked me to...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.83,0:09:38.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Please eliminate that family.”
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.00,0:09:42.90,Default,,0,0,0,,He's terrible to have a mistress...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.34,0:09:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,My mother was\Nsomeone's mistress, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.71,0:09:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,L-Listen.. never mind that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.34,0:09:52.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where the safe is,\Nin that house?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.11,0:09:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I believe it's in the back of the study\Non the 2nd floor.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.62,0:09:58.02,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.85,0:10:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor, you'd better get out\Nof here fast, tool
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.83,0:10:08.19,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know...?\NYou can erase the past.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.03,0:10:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,If you don't like it,\Nyou can erase everything...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.87,0:10:16.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can reset your life.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.94,0:10:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't think so. You may try to forget,\Nbut you cannot erase your past!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.78,0:10:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.85,0:10:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why I thought that...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.15,0:10:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did I think at that time that
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.52,0:10:36.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I could erase the past\Nby pulling this trigger?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.02,0:10:40.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder why I listened\Nto his request...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.40,0:10:47.77,Default,,0,0,0,,That's all I have to say. Please leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.94,0:10:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.14,0:10:57.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You're Dr. Tenma, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.98,0:11:03.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Please look at the message.\NIt's a message for you, from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.48,0:11:05.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You'll find it in the study of that house.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.82,0:11:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,What...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.52,0:11:10.58,Default,,0,0,0,,He knew that you would come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.06,0:11:16.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Erich said,\N“Your destiny is already determined.”
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.80,0:11:18.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Good-bye...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.17,0:11:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:27.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you, didn't I? Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.44,0:11:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,D-Don't tell me you...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.78,0:11:34.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, this is a suicide.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.55,0:11:36.98,Default,,0,0,0,,What the hell...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.62,0:11:45.75,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the use in dying?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.26,0:11:48.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's all over when you die.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.06,0:11:51.29,Default,,0,0,0,,There's nothing like living,\Nright, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.67,0:11:54.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... You sometimes say\Nsomething worthwhile, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.40,0:11:56.56,Default,,0,0,0,,What do you mean, sometimes?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:12:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,And so... you're after that unbelievable\Nserial killer named Johan?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.78,0:12:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't you forget about doing\Nsomething so stupid,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.78,0:12:06.94,Default,,0,0,0,,and team up with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.85,0:12:13.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh... By the way, when I tried to open\Nthis door earlier, I got the chills...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.80,0:12:31.77,Default,,0,0,0,,What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.24,0:12:38.27,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you shivering for, Doctor?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.35,0:12:42.75,Default,,0,0,0,,"Look at me! Look at me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.78,0:12:48.59,Default,,0,0,0,,"See how big the monster inside of me\Nhas grown, Dr. Tenma..."
Dialogue: 0,0:12:49.89,0:12:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Johan is... He is enjoying himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.13,0:12:58.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.19,0:13:03.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute! Listen to me!!\NHey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.90,0:13:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,I offered you a great deal.\NYou should be grateful.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.77,0:13:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,You promised to team up\Nwith me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.97,0:13:13.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Who said I'd team up with you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.98,0:13:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey! You need money in order\Nto run from the cops, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.12,0:13:28.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Get in the car!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.99,0:13:33.33,Default,,0,0,0,,This is your client.\NHe'll take you to your patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.70,0:13:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll hold on to your things.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.57,0:13:40.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you want them back,\Nyou'd better do your job, get paid,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.97,0:13:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,and come to Frank's place\Non Grasten Street.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.11,0:13:49.10,Default,,0,0,0,,So long. You'd better earn all you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.55,0:13:53.88,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a really profitable business.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.12,0:13:57.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, then... Since I got an advance,\NI guess I'll have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.02,0:14:04.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Counselor... I brought you a doctor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.73,0:14:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank goodness, Doctor... Hurry...\NPlease stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.44,0:14:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your axillary artery\Nhas been damaged.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.31,0:14:22.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get hit by a shotgun?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.88,0:14:26.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Hey, Doctor,\Nyou're empty-handed.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.65,0:14:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you get the surgical equipment?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.78,0:14:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,No. It was too dangerous in the city...\NI didn't get that far...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.66,0:14:36.63,Default,,0,0,0,,I couldn't operate on you here\Neven if I had the equipment.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.23,0:14:40.39,Default,,0,0,0,,You'd better get him to\Na proper doctor as soon as possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.46,0:14:43.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I would have done that if I could!\NHurry up and fix him!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.17,0:14:45.53,Default,,0,0,0,,How long ago was he shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.90,0:14:47.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Never mind the questions!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.68,0:14:55.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Four hours ago...?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:59.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Were you responsible for\Nthe terrorist attack this morning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.01,0:15:01.61,Default,,0,0,0,,What if we are?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.12,0:15:04.08,Default,,0,0,0,,I refuse!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.15,0:15:05.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Wha...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.89,0:15:06.95,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.56,0:15:09.61,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no desire\Nto treat anyone responsible
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.69,0:15:10.68,Default,,0,0,0,,for indiscriminate terrorist attacks!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:15.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't get funny! Do you realize\Nthe situation you're in now?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.26,0:15:17.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait a minute.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.57,0:15:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, Doc... Our friends will be\Ncoming to help us soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.37,0:15:25.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Just stop the bleeding by then,\Nwill you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.48,0:15:32.64,Default,,0,0,0,,What's with that attitude?!\NDo you want to die?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.98,0:15:34.54,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to wait up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.62,0:15:36.28,Default,,0,0,0,,B-But... Counselor...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.19,0:15:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,This doctor has my life\Nin his hands now...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.02,0:15:45.43,Default,,0,0,0,,If I should die...\NI want you to shoot him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.26,0:15:52.17,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not running a charity here,\Nyou know.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.30,0:15:56.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Pay us back the 250,000 marks\Nwe lent you, will you, Heckel?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.34,0:15:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Gross... I do intend\Nto pay you back...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.24,0:16:03.01,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nice. I'm glad you feel that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.41,0:16:07.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Just break both his arms for now.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.32,0:16:11.79,Default,,0,0,0,,I understand! I'll pay you back! I will!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.99,0:16:13.01,Default,,0,0,0,,Good boy...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,So, please wait another month...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.12,0:16:15.45,Monster - Radio,TV,0,0,0,,—In the random automatic rifle shooting
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:16.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Break both legs, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.52,0:16:16.85,Monster - Radio,TV,0,0,0,,—by terrorists this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.92,0:16:20.12,Monster - Radio,TV,0,0,0,,in Erfurt Station, witness accounts\Nhave helped police identify
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.19,0:16:24.79,Monster - Radio,TV,0,0,0,,the suspects as Max Steindorf\Nand Karl Blunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Please wait... Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.87,0:16:26.93,Monster - Radio,TV,0,0,0,,—The GWE has announced
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.00,0:16:29.33,Monster - Radio,TV,0,0,0,,that it will give anyone\Nwith promising leads on these two
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.40,0:16:31.96,Monster - Radio,TV,0,0,0,,a reward of 300,000 marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:33.37,0:16:34.77,Default,,0,0,0,,So, they were the ones...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.08,0:16:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?\NI can pay you back that money.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.21,0:16:39.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I know where those guys are!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.45,0:16:40.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That'll cancel out my debt to you!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.02,0:16:44.61,Default,,0,0,0,,That had better be the truth.\NOtherwise, I'll break your neck.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:44.69,0:16:46.59,Default,,0,0,0,,It's true! It's true! It's absolutely true!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.63,0:16:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, but Tenma's there right now...\NOh well...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.83,0:17:01.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You said what I did was
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.30,0:17:03.10,Default,,0,0,0,,an indiscriminate terrorist attack,\Ndidn't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.17,0:17:08.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That's ridiculous! There was\Na good reason for what I did...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.98,0:17:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that I've killed\Nthe president of GWE,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.25,0:17:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I could die tomorrow and I wouldn't mind.\NI feel so good.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.69,0:17:21.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Counselor...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.16,0:17:27.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I was a lawyer in East Germany...\NThis guy was secretary to a politician.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.03,0:17:30.50,Default,,0,0,0,,When the Wall came down,\Nwe all lost our jobs.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.43,0:17:34.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Doctor... Can you understand\Nhow we feel?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.60,0:17:42.57,Default,,0,0,0,,After the Wall fell, the GWE\Nused the power of money
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.64,0:17:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,to infiltrate into East Germany...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.71,0:17:50.88,Default,,0,0,0,,They aggressively built factories\Non our land... one after another...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.85,0:17:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,That is our country... I took pride\Nin shooting him. I took pride...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.86,0:18:03.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh! Counselor...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.13,0:18:06.79,Default,,0,0,0,,It's cold... so cold...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.97,0:18:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hang on!\NOur friends will be here soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.54,0:18:11.80,Default,,0,0,0,,They won't come.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.98,0:18:17.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Our friends won't come.\NI have a feeling...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.72,0:18:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop the bleeding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.12,0:18:25.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop it now! Or I'll shoot you dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.92,0:18:30.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll... kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.26,0:18:31.52,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.76,0:18:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.93,0:18:37.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to die...\NI don't want to die...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.97,0:18:46.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you afraid?\NAre you afraid to die?!?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.71,0:18:52.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they all died.\NThe twelve people you killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.05,0:18:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,That's how they...!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.58,0:18:58.55,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what it means, to kill someone!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.49,0:19:02.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Get me some disinfectant\Nand a pair of scissors.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.09,0:19:04.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.13,0:19:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,You have that much, don't you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.36,0:19:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Arterial bleeding... He's gone into\Nhypotensive shock.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.77,0:19:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I will use finger pressure on\Nthe damaged artery
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.27,0:19:17.24,Default,,0,0,0,,to stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.27,0:19:22.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I will suture the open flesh.\NNeedle and thread...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.24,0:19:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We haven't got anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.98,0:19:25.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Then a stapler will do!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.45,0:19:26.71,Default,,0,0,0,,A stapler...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.11,0:19:28.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get it!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.15,0:19:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.23,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.84,0:19:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.34,0:19:50.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you going to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.61,0:19:53.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I applied first aid.\NI'm taking him to a hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.48,0:19:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,A-A hospital?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.81,0:20:03.18,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you thinking?!\NIf you don't put him down, I'll kill you!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.32,0:20:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Shoot me if you want!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.49,0:20:10.79,Default,,0,0,0,,If you're going to shoot me,\Nthen you take this guy to the hospital.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.08,0:20:32.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Put me down here...\NYou get out of here...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.58,0:20:38.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I remembered a while ago... I thought\NI'd seen your face somewhere before.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.25,0:20:42.78,Default,,0,0,0,,You're that doctor who's wanted\Nin those serial killings, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.82,0:20:44.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and put me down!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.06,0:20:52.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What I did was not\Nan indiscriminate terrorist attack.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.27,0:20:58.93,Default,,0,0,0,,The guys I killed were the president\Nof GWE, his lackeys,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.01,0:21:00.10,Default,,0,0,0,,and his bodyguards.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.98,0:21:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,So you're saying that there were\Nno unintended victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.21,0:21:08.41,Default,,0,0,0,,You mean the girl\Nwho was at the newsstand?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.52,0:21:13.18,Default,,0,0,0,,So, you did know about it...\NThat you had shot her.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.12,0:21:19.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save a man like me?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.49,0:21:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because you were afraid you\Nwere going to be killed, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:24.47,0:21:27.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Your eyes tell me you weren't afraid\Nof being killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.14,0:21:33.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Why did you save\Nthis indiscriminate terrorist... this killer?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.58,0:21:37.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Because I believed you...\NThat you were a human being.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.52,0:21:43.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and go!\NThe police will be here...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.15,0:21:46.12,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to live...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.33,0:21:52.29,Default,,0,0,0,,You...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.16,0:21:55.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're a brilliant doctor...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:00.47,0:22:02.99,Default,,0,0,0,,So what happened to the money?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.07,0:22:05.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me you fixed him and just left!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.27,0:22:07.74,Monster - Radio,TV,0,0,0,,—The perpetrators of the terrorist attack
Dialogue: 0,0:22:07.81,0:22:10.51,Monster - Radio,TV,0,0,0,,this morning at Erfurt Station\Nhave been captured.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.15,0:22:13.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Say something, will you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.15,0:22:13.58,Monster - Radio,TV,0,0,0,,—Police anticipated strong resistance.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.85,0:22:17.75,Monster - Radio,TV,0,0,0,,But it seems they surrendered\Nwithout a fight.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.22,0:22:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,We're not running\Na charity here, you... Hey...!
